    • The fishstatR package

    fishstatR

    The fishstatR package provides reference data from an EBX5database ready to use for applications. For communication with EBX5 it uses the package faoebx5. For statisticians, it allows to have access to up-to-date reference data; inlcuding for shiny applications.

    Installation

    The latest development version can be installed from github:

    install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github('bergert/fishstatr')

    Functions

    If you come from github: Reference/Getting started:

    fishstatR Please, refer to the Reference tab for more details about the functions, or you can start with examples on the page Getting started.
